# Netlify Redirects
# This file is copied into dist/public by Vite at build time.
# It has highest priority in Netlify's redirect processing.
#
# Rule 1: Proxy all /api/* requests to Railway backend (server-side, no CORS)
#   - status=200 means Netlify PROXIES the request (browser sees taskspaceweb.netlify.app)
#   - :splat captures everything after /api/
/api/*  https://happy-consideration-production.up.railway.app/api/:splat  200

# Rule 2: SPA fallback — send all other routes to index.html (React Router)
/*  /index.html  200
